title: Cross-version ConceptMap for FHIR R5 resources in FHIR R4
description: This ConceptMap represents the cross-version mapping of resource FHIR R5 for use in FHIR R4.

target.comment:
FHIR R5 Resource `DeviceDefinition` is representable via FHIR R4 Resource `DeviceDefinition`.
Element `DeviceDefinition` has is mapped to FHIR R4 element `DeviceDefinition`, but has no comparisons.
Element `DeviceDefinition.meta` has is mapped to FHIR R4 element `DeviceDefinition.meta`, but has no comparisons.

Element `DeviceDefinition.contained` has is mapped to FHIR R4 element `DeviceDefinition.contained`, but has no comparisons.
Element `DeviceDefinition.description` has a context of DeviceDefinition based on following the parent source element upwards and mapping to `DeviceDefinition`.
Element `DeviceDefinition.identifier` has is mapped to FHIR R4 element `DeviceDefinition.identifier`, but has no comparisons.

Element `DeviceDefinition.udiDeviceIdentifier` has is mapped to FHIR R4 element `DeviceDefinition.udiDeviceIdentifier`, but has no comparisons.
Note available implied context: `DeviceDefinition.packaging.udiDeviceIdentifier` because `DeviceDefinition.packaging.udiDeviceIdentifier` is defined as a content reference to `DeviceDefinition.udiDeviceIdentifier`.

Element `DeviceDefinition.udiDeviceIdentifier.deviceIdentifier` is part of an existing definition because parent element `DeviceDefinition.udiDeviceIdentifier` requires a cross-version extension.
